Class CouponDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.hit.couponstorem.model.CouponDao
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICouponDao

    public class CouponDao
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICouponDao
    This class implements the Data Access Object for the class Coupon. This class holds methods for connecting to the Data Base MySQL and retrieving data that corresponds to the class Coupon.
